#define CheckBlackAdam ["He's looking for a fight. Should we oblige?","He’s calling us out, Adam. Are you going to answer?","He’s spoiling for a brawl. Any suggestions on how to handle him?","Abomination! You are far from home. Stand down.","He seems focused on you, Adam. Probably wants to prove he’s the strongest.","You're awfully quiet, Adam. Waiting for the right moment?","He’s definitely persistent. I’ll take the front, you flank him?"]

